一、定义 / 1. Definitions
-------------------------
1. "本软件" 指 Adnify 及其所有源代码、文档、资源文件和相关材料。
   "Software" refers to Adnify and all its source code, documentation, 
   resource files, and related materials.

2. "作者" 指 adnaan (adnaan.worker@gmail.com)。
   "Author" refers to adnaan (adnaan.worker@gmail.com).

3. "商业使用" 指任何以营利为目的的使用，包括但不限于：销售、出租、
   提供付费服务、集成到商业产品中等。
   "Commercial Use" means any use for profit, including but not limited to: 
   selling, renting, providing paid services, integrating into commercial 
   products, etc.

4. "非商业使用" 指个人学习、研究、教育或非营利组织的内部使用。
   "Non-Commercial Use" means personal learning, research, education, or 
   internal use by non-profit organizations.

